                <li>Mobile app—Sebastian could do sessions from anywhere on campus with decent Wi-Fi</li>
                <li>Reliable video quality even on spotty university internet (mostly—there was one session that froze halfway through)</li>
                <li>Therapist matching connected him with Dr. Park who specialized in academic anxiety and first-gen student issues</li>
                <li>Digital worksheets and thought logs that integrated into his already-digital workflow (everything in Google Drive)</li>
              </ul>
